### 请求 /cps/freeze/config/create 接口 => 成功（全局冻结配置）
POST {{baseUrl}}/cps/freeze/config/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

{
  "platformCode": null,
  "unfreezeDays": 15,
  "status": 1,
  "remark": "全局默认配置-确认收货后15天解冻"
}

### 请求 /cps/freeze/config/create 接口 => 成功（京东专属冻结配置）
POST {{baseUrl}}/cps/freeze/config/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

{
  "platformCode": "jd",
  "unfreezeDays": 7,
  "status": 1,
  "remark": "京东-确认收货后7天解冻"
}

### 请求 /cps/freeze/config/update 接口 => 成功
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cps/freeze/config/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

{
  "id": 1,
  "unfreezeDays": 20,
  "status": 1,
  "remark": "修改为20天解冻"
}

### 请求 /cps/freeze/config/delete 接口 => 成功
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cps/freeze/config/delete?id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/freeze/config/page 接口 => 成功
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/freeze/config/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/freeze/config/page 接口 => 按平台筛选
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/freeze/config/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=10&platformCode=taobao
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/freeze/record/page 接口 => 成功
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/freeze/record/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/freeze/record/page 接口 => 按会员+冻结状态筛选
GET {{baseUrl}}/cps/freeze/record/page?pageNo=1&pageSize=10&memberId=1001&freezeStatus=frozen
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}

### 请求 /cps/freeze/record/manual-unfreeze 接口 => 成功（手动解冻）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cps/freeze/record/manual-unfreeze?id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
tenant-id: {{adminTenantId}}
